description: Package that adds core Qt 4.8.3 libraries into your BlackBerry application targetting PlayBook v2.1 and newer versions.
releaseNotes: This is the first release of the package. One of following Visual Studio extensions is required to build and deploy the project. You can find more info at: https://github.com/phofman/vs-plugin
title: Qt 4.8.3 Core for PlayBook
